snippet.title: AirMech PAX Trailer
snippet.description:
Play AirMech now: http://airmech.com

What could you do with a giant, flying, transforming mech? Anything you want! Get ready to pilot your AirMech, the ultimate battlefield weapon. Change between transporting tanks and smashing the enemy in the blink of an eye. Shoot, slice, and stomp your way through enemy hordes, or built your own huge army to unleash. Strategy has never been so action packed!

Music: Killing Grounds by Front Line Assembly: http://airme.ch/1f0yBm7

Video edited by Exophic: http://www.youtube.com/user/Exophic
